---
title: Coconut Red Curry Chicken with Fragrant Rice and Crispy Shallots
description: Tonight, creamy coconut red curry chicken is spooned over fragrant rice for an unforgettable aromatic experience! The mild curry paste makes it suitable for anyone who's shy with spice!
